The '''Shard of Alderaan''' was a [[Slicer/Legends|slicing]] program created by the [[Alderaanian/Legends|Alderaanian]] slicer known only as "[[Never Die]]." It ended up in the hands of [[Begas Tok]], who stole it from the slicer. Tok intended to auction the Shard of [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]] off, in order to pay off his debts to [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba the Hutt]]. The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] and the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] both sent representatives to the meeting to attempt to gain control of the Shard. Never Die also sent his droid [[0-1B]], disguised as a medical droid, to retrieve or destroy the program.

